<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Your Flower Shop</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@20..48,100..700,0..1,-50..200" />
    <!-- <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css" type="text/css"> -->

    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f7f7f7;
            color: #333;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #4caf50;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 1rem;
        }

        section {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        h2 {
            color: #4caf50;
        }
        h1 {
          font-size: 2.5rem;
        }
        p {
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        footer {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 0;
            width: 100%;
        }
        .btn-orchids {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #4caf50;
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }

        .btn-orchids:hover {
            background-color: #45a049;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Orchids Flower Shop</h1>
    </header>

    <section>
        <h2>Welcome to Orchid Flower Shop!</h2>
        <p>At Orchids Flower Shop, we provide a wide variety of fresh and vibrant flowers for all occasions. Whether you're celebrating a special event, expressing love, or just want to brighten someone's day, we have the perfect bouquet for you.</p>

        <p>Explore our collection and discover the beauty of our handpicked flowers. We also offer reliable delivery services to make sure your flowers reach their destination on time.</p>
        <a href="/orchids" class="btn-orchids">
          <span>Move to orchids page</span>
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined">
            arrow_forward
            </span>
        </a>

    </section>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 Your Flower Shop. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html> 